{"tid":1003971,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好心唔撚識剪頭髮就咪撚害人","createTime":"2019-02-01T05:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T09:01:35.000Z","uid":185842,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3504cc5b13e9b0805310ee5ea91168671f1b0087","tid":1003971,"uid":185842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T05:52:43.000Z","msg":"一入到去就同我講，剪頭髮先無人幫手洗頭住，屌！頭髮唔洗就一定剪得無咁順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好彩我做完運動洗咗頭，費時曬時間就由佢，然後問我點剪，同佢講想留前面個陰加兩邊個頂留翻多啲，其他跟個形剪。<br />\n<br />\n屌！第一下就同我剷咗上去，我喝住佢叫佢咪咁上，點知佢喝翻我轉頭，我個下真係好想爆，唔好同我講咪又係睇死我毒撚唔敢爆，我只係唔想個頭再7落佢。<br />\n<br />\n一開始同佢講想啲陰留落嚟，宜家咪又係短到要all back個隻！<br />\n<br />\n成程識用個剷，一係就係咁快刀手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，咪又係唔撚識剪。<br />\n<br />\n最抵死係最尾竟然比卡片我，我當堂撕爛咗，同佢講:你剪到咁7唔係要我再搵你呀？<br />\n<br />\n最後我想問 邊到有靚菠蘿買，想補一補個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d14f92daed0ab99b0de6aa39b9b42c2b715c318","tid":1003971,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T05:53:43.000Z","msg":"邊間"},{"pid":"c47d79aa5b1d0c5ded6a61c8cddf7d7ff66aacb5","tid":1003971,"uid":72327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T05:58:11.000Z","msg":"開名啦<br />\n<br />\n雖然我個頭7開<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac47f7a7f9f3ca9581a632ad1d5b562f883f497","tid":1003971,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T06:00:03.000Z","msg":"樣7先要留陰<br />\n講左咩 自己諗下"},{"pid":"98213e45b7958ae944edd39acaf7b21e38c9c02c","tid":1003971,"uid":205844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T06:15:07.000Z","msg":"去街市買飯碗cup住算啦，菠蘿咁貴"},{"pid":"96fdabb49ab551a35569f776210e900b396b682f","tid":1003971,"uid":185842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"aac47f7a7f9f3ca9581a632ad1d5b562f883f497","tid":1003971,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T06:00:03.